sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSP Driver)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL / PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: ML Pipeline Metadata Recording
    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution(execution, artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>MySQL/PG wire protocol | Optional SSL | Username/Password
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT INTO Execution, Artifact, Event, ...
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (rows inserted)
    MLMD->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse(execution_id, artifact_ids)

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1b: Type Registration
    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifactType(type_name, properties)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Optional TLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT from Type table (check existing)
    DB-->>MLMD: Existing type or empty
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE Type with schema evolution
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactTypeResponse(type_id)

    participant Client as ML Pipeline UI / Client

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query
    Client->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(starting_nodes, depth, direction)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts, executions, events (graph traversal)<br/>MySQL/PG wire protocol | Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Result rows (entities + relationships)
    MLMD-->>Client: LineageGraph(artifacts, executions, events, contexts)

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2b: Artifact Lookup
    Client->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext(context_id, filter)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 | Optional TLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with ZetaSQL-parsed filter<br/>MySQL/PG wire protocol | Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: Matching artifact rows
    MLMD-->>Client: GetArtifactsResponse(artifacts, next_page_token)
